org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.css.codegen

Interface ICSSRuntimeConstants


  • public interface ICSSRuntimeConstants
    Defines all the runtime constants in the CSS framework. The constants are of type Integer so that they can be directly used in InstructionList.addInstruction(int, Object).
